      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 22.12 - 老子 22.13</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 22.12</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫唯不爭，故天下莫能與之爭。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>It is because he is thus free from striving that therefore no one in the world is able to strive with him.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
