      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 22.14 - 老子 22.15</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 22.13</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>古之所謂曲則全者，豈虛言哉！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>That saying of the ancients that 'the partial becomes complete' was not vainly spoken:</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
